pageContext.claim: “So hard to watch @FoxNews anymore. They are working so hard against the people (viewers) that got them there. Their contributors are a disaster, and all over the place. The Radical Left has scared Fox into submission, just like they have so many others. Sad, but we will WIN!”
pageContext.analysis: Fox News is Trump's biggest cheerleader, with an army of hosts who sing his praises every night.
